  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The <code>autostart</code> target describes services that should start with a fresh user session.
Or it will eventually.
Mostly I&rsquo;m just working on a reproducible setup for <a href="https://github.com/jceb/dex">dex</a>.</p>
